{"word":"H4803 - מָרַט - mâraṭ - maw-rat' - Bright","slug":"H4803","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָרַט</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâraṭ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-rat'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bright"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E8;&#x05D8; - ma&#x0302;rat&#x0323;</b> - <i>maw-rat'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>polish</i>; by implication to <i>make bald</i> (the head), to <i>gall</i> (the shoulder); also, to <i>sharpen: - </i>bright, furbish, (have his) hair (be) fallen off, peeled, pluck off (hair.)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4178\">H4178</a>, <a href=\"#/H4179\">H4179</a>, <a href=\"#/H4593\">H4593</a>, <a href=\"#/H4811\">H4811</a>, <a href=\"#/H4812\">H4812</a>, <a href=\"#/H4813\">H4813</a>, <a href=\"#/H4821\">H4821</a>, <a href=\"#/H4822\">H4822</a>, <a href=\"#/H4824\">H4824</a>, <a href=\"#/H4825\">H4825</a>, <a href=\"#/H4826\">H4826</a>, <a href=\"#/H4831\">H4831</a>"}]}